  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the effectiveness of pharmaceutical care, compared
      to usual care, in patient discharge in an emergency department in patients with hypertension
      and/or diabetes mellitus type 2.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
